41
00:04:21,652 --> 00:04:29,260
So are we eating in a world that Lee Young Ja has created?

42
00:04:30,078 --> 00:04:32,439
Then, I'm going to eat something else.

43
00:04:34,474 --> 00:04:39,345
Don't try to get out of the box.

44
00:05:02,651 --> 00:05:05,113
Did something bad happen?

45
