Are you going on a trip?

54
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,750
Yes.

55
00:06:03,750 --> 00:06:05,260
With your girlfriend?

56
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:07,908
No, with a boyfriend.

57
00:06:07,908 --> 00:06:13,138
You know fireworks are a must when you guys travel together through Yeongdong Highway, right?

58
00:06:13,138 --> 00:06:16,801
Isn't it illegal to light fireworks on the beach these days?

59
00:06:16,801 --> 00:06:19,662
That's why they don't sell it on the beach, but we do here.

60
00:06:20,913 --> 00:06:23,074
Let me see.

61
