94
00:09:45,426 --> 00:09:47,286
Why?

95
00:09:47,286 --> 00:09:51,940
When I was in elementary school, I was a boy scout.

96
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:55,436
But one day, Joon Pyo forced me to join the Sea Cadets.

97
00:09:55,436 --> 00:09:58,948
I was in the Sea Cadets too.

98
00:10:01,884 --> 00:10:08,508
But the kids from other schools hazed me in the ocean.

99
00:10:10,601 --> 00:10:14,897
With you was my first time back to the ocean after that.

100
00:10:17,875 --> 00:10:25,124
