How's it going with Ae Ri?

111
00:11:34,619 --> 00:11:38,414
Ae Ri? We're just friends.

112
00:11:40,066 --> 00:11:43,561
You should've walked Ae Ri home that night. Why did you walk me home?

113
00:11:43,561 --> 00:11:45,596
Don't you have any common sense?

114
00:11:46,739 --> 00:11:51,510
Ae Ri doesn't like to be treated like that. And we are just friends!

115
00:11:52,170 --> 00:11:57,934
When I ask about your relationship, does it make me seem like a nosy old man?

116
00:11:57,934 --> 00:12:00,895
Yes, a little bit.

117
00:12:03,239 --> 00:12:10,304
Why did you want to come to the beach with me? You have a lot of friends.

118
00:12:12,597 --> 00:12:15,476
It's because you don't know me well.

119
00:12:17,119 --> 00:12:18,780
What does that mean?

120
00:12:18,780 --> 00:12:20,580
It's literal.

121
00:12:20,580 --> 00:12:25,750
I feel more comfortable around you because you don't know all my baggage.

122
00:12:31,233 --> 00:12:32,968
Jae Won.

123
00:12:34,787 --> 00:12:36,322
Nothing.

124
00:12:36,322 --> 00:12:40,184
Why? What was it?

125
00:12:40,184 --> 00:12:42,286
I just called your name for no reason.

126
00:12:42,987 --> 00:12:46,924
Wait, are you coaxing out my answer like this?

127
00:12:46,924 --> 00:12:48,642
It's not like that.

128
00:12:48,642 --> 00:12:53,664
You are slyer than I expected. I was almost fooled.

129
00:12:55,458 --> 00:12:59,044
