133
00:13:12,658 --> 00:13:15,820
Something like your water torture story?

134
00:13:15,820 --> 00:13:17,310
Hyung!

135
00:13:17,310 --> 00:13:18,520
I'm just kidding.

136
00:13:18,523 --> 00:13:22,001
