137
00:13:22,001 --> 00:13:24,203
How do you know that?

138
00:13:26,964 --> 00:13:29,858
It's because you're so pure.

139
00:13:34,130 --> 00:13:36,591
You seem to have a lot on your mind.

140
00:13:37,850 --> 00:13:39,868
Right?

141
