143
00:14:00,472 --> 00:14:03,543
I learned it from Ae Ri. So stand right there, and I'll take a good one.

144
00:14:03,543 --> 00:14:05,285
Really?

145
00:14:47,728 --> 00:14:49,463
Are you okay?

146
00:14:51,857 --> 00:14:55,202
They actually sell this type of stuff here.

147
00:14:55,202 --> 00:14:58,013
I think you overdid it.

148
